This paper involves natural language processing (NLP) and image analysis using deep learning models, which are commonly studied in the computer science sub-categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of attention mechanisms in the models also suggests a focus on interpretability and explainability, which are important topics in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
